  <name>YapCap</name>
  <summary>COSMIC panel applet for Codex, Claude Code, and Cursor usage</summary>
  <description>
    <p>YapCap is a native COSMIC panel applet that tracks your AI coding quota for Codex, Claude Code, and Cursor right from the panel. Add accounts once and YapCap fetches usage directly from provider APIs. No telemetry, no cloud sync, no separate service account required.</p>
    <p>Use the popup to compare multiple accounts, see which CLI account is active, switch panel styles, and follow your COSMIC light, dark, and accent color settings.</p>
    <p>Main features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Codex usage tracking and credits</li>
      <li>Claude usage tracking and extra usage meter</li>
      <li>Cursor usage tracking: API, Composer and Total</li>
      <li>Multiple accounts per provider</li>
      <li>Active account badge</li>
      <li>COSMIC theme integration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
